title: Keb' Mo' - 1996 - Just Like You (2002 SACD 24 88.2) FLAC
description:
Keb' Mo' - 1996 - Just Like You
2002 SACD 24 bits, 88.2 KHz

On his second album, Keb' Mo' begins to expand the borders of his Delta blues by recording with a full band on a couple of tracks and attempting more expansive, rock-based song structures. The attempts aren't entirely successful and it's ironic that he decided to try rock-oriented material after he received such praise for his traditionalist debut. Still, there are a few songs on the album that rank with the best on his first album, which suggests that Just Like You is merely a sophomore slump. (AllMusic)
